<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.5389.2.10>
    dc:creator "Sites, Robert W." ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Maculambrysus Reynoso & Sites, 2021 (Hemiptera: Heteroptera: Naucoridae) from an aguaje palm swamp in southeastern Peru" ;
    bibo:endPage "294" ;
    bibo:issue "2" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2023-12-19" ;
    bibo:startPage "288" ;
    bibo:volume "5389" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10406818>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10406820>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10406822> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10406818>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–4. Maculambrysus gallicei n.sp. (1) Holotype dorsal habitus, (2) holotype ventral habitus, (3) male terminal abdominal terga, arrow indicates accessory genitalic process of tergum VI, (4) male abdominal tergum VIII." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10406818/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10406820>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5–11. Maculambrysus gallicei n.sp. (5–6) Male genital capsule with and without terga IX and X, respectively, (7) male left paramere, (8–10) male phallosoma in right, ventral, and left aspects, respectively (11) female terminal abdominal sterna, white arrow indicates production on posterior margin of right laterosternite VI, yellow arrow indicates small, digitate production at posteromedial corner of left laterosternite VI. sgp = subgenital plate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10406820/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10406822>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12–13. Type locality of Maculambrysus gallicei n.sp. (12) Aguaje palm swamp, (13) pools on muddy trail near aguaje palm swamp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10406822/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

